il]]|[[Anders Aukland]]|[[\u00d8yvind Skaanes]]}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Men 4x10 km Relay C \u2013 Beitost\u00f8len|url=http://skisport365.com/ski/resultat.php?lop=703|publisher=skisport365.com|accessdate=20 March 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=center|2\n| align=right|11 January 1998 &nbsp;\n| {{flagicon|AUT}} [[Ramsau am Dachstein|Ramsau]]\n| align=right|4 \u00d7 10&nbsp;km relay C/F &nbsp;\n| {{Relay|{{ITA}} |[[Fabio Maj]]|[[Fulvio Valbusa]]|[[Pietro Piller Cottrer]]|[[Silvio Fauner]]}}\n| {{Relay|{{SWE}} |[[Mathias Fredriksson]]|[[Niklas Jonsson]]|[[Per Elofsson]]|[[Torgny Mogren]]}}\n| {{Relay|{{AUT}} |[[Mikhail Botvinov]]|[[Alois Stadlober]]|[[Christian Hoffmann]]|[[Achim Walcher]]}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Men 4x10 km Relay \u2013 Ramsau|url=http://skisport365.com/ski/resultat.php?lop=702|publisher=Skisport365.com|accessdate=20 March 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=center|3\n| align=right|6 March 1998 &nbsp;\n| {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Lahti]]\n| align=right|4 \u00d7 10&nbsp;km relay C/F &nbsp;\n|{{Relay|{{FIN}} I|[[Harri Kirvesniemi]]|[[Mika Myllyl\u00e4]]|[[Sami Repo]]|[[Jari Isomets\u00e4]]}}\n|{{Relay|{{NOR}} |[[Frode Estil]]|[[Sture Sivertsen]]|[[Anders Eide]]|[[Thomas Alsgaard]]}}\n|{{Relay|{{RUS}} I|[[Vladimir Legotine]]|[[Alexey Prokurorov]]|[[Andrey Noutrikhin]]|[[Sergey Chepikov]]}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Men 4x10 km Relay C/F \u2013 Lahti|url=http://skisport365.com/ski/resultat.php?lop=701|publisher=Skisport365.com|accessdate=20 March 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=center|4\n| align=right|10 March 1998 &nbsp;\n| {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Falun]]\n| align=right|Team sprint C/F &nbsp;\n| {{Relay|{{SWE}} I|[[Mathias Fredriksson]]|[[Per Elofsson]]}}\n| {{Relay|{{NOR}} |[[Rune Torseth]]|[[Tor Arne Hetland]]}}\n| {{Relay|{{FIN}} I|[[Jari Isomets\u00e4]]|[[Ari Palolahti]]}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Men's Team Sprint (10x1.6 km) C/F \u2013 Falun|url=http://skisport365.com/ski/resultat.php?lop=700|publisher=Skisport365.com|accessdate=20 March 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Ladies' team ===\n