l 10, 2020 |quote=Robert Parker, with the Virginia Department of Health told WHSV that the only information that can be provided, to protect patient privacy, is the health district in which the person lived.}}</ref>\n<!--Do NOT change the disease totals UNLESS YOU HAVE A SOURCE. PERIOD.-->\n<onlyinclude>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:right\" \n! colspan=\"3\" |COVID-19 Deaths in Virginia<ref name=\"VDHSituationSummary1\" /><ref name=\"WSLS-March 27\"/><ref name=\"WTVR-March22\"/><br>\nUpdated April 13, 2020\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" |Health district\n! scope=\"col\" |Deaths\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Alexandria Health District{{efn|Alexandria: Includes all of the City of Alexandria.<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 1<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Alleghany Health District{{efn|Alleghany Health District: Includes Alleghany County, Botetourt County, Craig County, Roanoke County, Covington City, Salem City<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 2<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Arlington Health District{{efn|Arlington Health District: Includes all of Arlington County<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 11<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Central Shenandoah Health District{{efn|Central Shenandoah Health District: Augusta County, Bath County, Highland County, Rockbridge County, Rockingham County, plus the cities of Buena Vista, Harrisonburg, Lexington, Staunton, and Waynesboro<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 1<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Central Virginia Health District{{efn|Central Virginia Health District: Includes Amherst County, Appomattox County, Bedford County, Campbell County, Lynchburg City<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 1<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Chesapeake Health District{{efn|Chesapeake He