ID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Henrico Health District{{efn|Henrico Health District: Henrico County and all cities/towns within the County<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 45<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Lenowisco Health District{{efn|Lenowisco Health District: Includes Lee County, Scott County, Wise County, Norton City<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 1<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Loudoun Health District{{efn|Loudoun Health District: Loudoun County and all cities/towns within the County<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 5<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Mount Rogers Health District{{efn|Mount Rogers Health District: Includes Bland County, Carroll County, Grayson County, Smyth County, Washington County, Wythe County, Bristol City, Galax City<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 5<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Norfolk Health District{{efn|Norfolk Health District: Includes Norfolk City<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 1<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Peninsula Health District{{efn|Peninsula Health District: Newport News, Poquoson, Williamsburg, James City County, York County<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 11<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Piedmont Health District{{efn|Piedmont Health District: Includes Amelia County, Buckingham County, Charlotte County, Cumberland County, Lunenburg County, Nottoway County, Prince Edward County<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 2<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Pittsylvania Health District{{efn|Pittsylvania Health District: Includes Pittsylvania County, Danville City<ref name=\"Local Health Districts\"/>}}\n| 1<ref name=\"COVID-19 in Virginia\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-